                 <table>
                  <tr>
                   <td class="statText" colspan="2">
                    We can obtain the answer in the following steps:
                    <ol>
                     <li>
                      ES[PRI]T -&gt; ESIPR
                     </li>
                     <li>
                      E[SIP]R -&gt; EIPS
                     </li>
                     <li>
                      [EIP]S -&gt; EIP
                     </li>
                    </ol>
                   </td>
                  </tr>
                 </table>
